		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Super Scope and the Justifier register &quot;hits&quot; from the scanlines on the screen totally differently,<br />plus the super scope has 2 more buttons that the Justifier does not. I had the same dream at one<br />point and then, as I am telling you now, I had it explained to me it wasn't a dream it's a nightmare. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_sad.gif" alt=":(" title="Sad" />

		

